#include<string>

#include<cstdlib>
using namespace std;
int days1[13]={0,31,60,91,121,152,182,213,244,274,305,335,366};
int days0[13]={0,31,59,90,120,151,181,212,243,273,304,334,365};
int leapyear(int n)
{
    //cout<<n<<endl;
    if(n%400==0||(n%4==0&&n%100!=0))return 1;
    else return 0;
}
int main()
{
  int testcases;
  char s[15],month[5];
  cin>>testcases;
  for(int i=0;i<testcases;i++){
     cin>> s;
     int date=(s[0]-48)*10+s[1]-48;
     int year=(s[7]-48)*1000+(s[8]-48)*100+(s[9]-48)*10+(s[10]-48);
     month[0]=s[3];month[1]=s[4];month[2]=s[5];month[3]='\0';
     int leap=leapyear(year);
     //cout<<leap<<endl;
     cout<<"Case "<<i+1<<": ";
     if(strcmp(month,"JAN")==0){cout<<date<<" Hundreds"<<endl;}
     else if(strcmp(month,"FEB")==0){cout<<(31+date)<<" Hundreds"<<endl;}
     else if(strcmp(month,"MAR")==0){if(leap==1)cout<<days1[2]+date<<" Hundreds"<<endl;
                           else cout<<days0[2]+date<<" Hundreds"<<endl;
                          }
     else if(strcmp(month,"APR")==0){if(leap==1)cout<<days1[3]+date<<" Hundreds"<<endl;
                         else cout<<days0[3]+date<<" Hundreds"<<endl;
                        }
     else if(strcmp(month,"MAY")==0){if(leap==1)cout<<days1[4]+date<<" Hundreds"<<endl;
                         else cout<<days0[4]+date<<" Hundreds"<<endl;
                        }
     else if(strcmp(month,"JUN")==0){if(leap==1)cout<<days1[5]+date<<" Hundreds"<<endl;
                         else cout<<days0[5]+date<<" Hundreds"<<endl;
                        }
    else if(strcmp(month,"JUL")==0){if(leap==1)cout<<days1[6]+date<<" Hundreds"<<endl;
                         else cout<<days0[6]+date<<" Hundreds"<<endl;
                        }
    else if(strcmp(month,"AUG")==0){if(leap==1)cout<<days1[7]+date<<" Hundreds"<<endl;
                         else cout<<days0[7]+date<<" Hundreds"<<endl;
                        }
   else if(strcmp(month,"SEP")==0){if(leap==1)cout<<days1[8]+date<<" Hundreds"<<endl;
                         else cout<<days0[8]+date<<" Hundreds"<<endl;
                        }
   else if(strcmp(month,"OCT")==0){if(leap==1){if(days1[9]+date>300)cout<<days1[9]+date-300<<" Tens"<<endl;
                                     else cout<<days1[9]+date<<" Hundreds"<<endl;
                                     }
                         else {if(days0[9]+date>300)cout<<days0[9]+date-300<<" Tens"<<endl;
                               else cout<<days0[9]+date<<" Hundreds"<<endl;
                              }
                        }
   else if(strcmp(month,"NOV")==0){if(leap==1)cout<<days1[10]+date-300<<" Tens"<<endl;
                         else cout<<days0[10]+date-300<<" Tens"<<endl;
                        }
   else if(strcmp(month,"DEC")==0){if(leap==1){if(days1[11]+date>360)cout<<days1[11]+date-360<<" Ones"<<endl;
                                     else cout<<days1[11]+date-300<<" Tens"<<endl;
                                    }
                         else {if(days0[11]+date>360)cout<<days0[11]+date-360<<" Ones"<<endl;
                               else cout<<days0[11]+date-300<<" Tens"<<endl;
                              }

                         }
  }
 return 0;
}
